one auto.</strong><br />\r\n			Trasferimento in aeroporto, volo di ritorno.</p>\r\n\r\n			<p><strong><em>Fine dei nostril servizi…</em></strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n', '14', 'App\Models\Tour');
INSERT INTO translations (locale, column_name, value, translatable_id, translatable_type) VALUES ('en', 'route_lines', '<img alt=\"\" class=\"content-block\" src=\"images/316/route-3.jpg\" />\r\n<table class=\"table tour-table-rounded\">\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th style=\"width:8%;\">Days</th>\r\n			<th style=\"width:14%;\">Waypoint</th>\r\n			<th style=\"width:8%;\">Time</th>\r\n			<th>Subjects of itinerary</th>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td rowspan=\"2\">DAY 1</td>\r\n			<td rowspan=\"2\">Tashkent</td>\r\n			<td>AM</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>Arrival Tashkent, accommodation at hotel. Car Rental procedures.</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>PM</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><strong>Lunch.</strong><br />\r\n			<strong><em>Sightseeing tour in Tashkent;</em></strong> Kukeldash Madrassah, Kaffal Shashi Mausoleum, Barak Khan Madrassah, Mosque on Khasty Imam Street, Visit to Chor-Su – oriental market (handicraft bazaar).<br />\r\n			<strong>Dinner.</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td rowspan=\"2\">DAY 2</td>\r\n			<td rowspan=\"2\">Tashkent – Sentab</td>\r\n			<td>AM</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><strong>Breakfast.</strong><br />\r\n			Drive to Sentab village 310 km. Arrival and accommodation at homestay.<br />\r\n			<strong>Lunch.</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>PM</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>Sightseeing of the village<br />\r\n			<strong>Dinner (included).</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td rowspan=\"2\">DAY 3</td>\r\n			<td rowspan=\"2\">\r\n			<p><strong><em>Sentab – </em></strong><br />\r\n			<strong><em>Yurt Camp</em></strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>AM</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><strong>Breakfast.</strong><br />\r\n			Short trekking in Nurata Mountain Reserve.</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>PM</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><strong>Lunch pick nick </strong><strong>included.</strong><br />\r\n			From Sentab drive to yurt camp, 120 km. Arrival to yurt camp and accommodation in a yurt. Short camel back riding.<br />\r\n			<strong>Dinner around the fire with folk performance (included). </strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td rowspan=\"2\">DAY 4</td>\r\n			<td rowspan=\"2\">Yurt Camp -Bukhara</td>\r\n			<td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><strong>Breakfast.</strong><br />\r\n			Free at leisure time. You may explore desert, drive to Aydarkul lake.&nbsp;</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><strong>Lunch pick nick at the shore of Aydarkul Lake (</strong><strong>included). </strong><br />\r\n			Drive to Bukhara via Nurata town. Visit ruins of Alexander the Great fortress and Chashma Mosque. En route visit petroglyphs.<br />\r\n			Arrival to Bukhara in the evening.<br />\r\n			<strong>Distance 240 km</strong><br />\r\n			<strong>Dinner.</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td rowspan=\"2\">DAY 5</td>\r\n			<td rowspan=\"2\">Bukhara</td>\r\n			<td>AM</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><strong>Breakfast.</strong><br />\r\n			<strong><em>Sightseeing tour in Bukhara:</em></strong> Poi-Kalyan Ensemble including Minaret (12c) Mosque (15c), functioning Madrassah Miri-Arab (16 c), Emir-Alim-Khan Madrassah (14c), Taqi (trading domes), Kukeldash Madrassah (16c), Nadir Divanbegi (17c), Magok-i-Attari Mosque(16c), Lyab-i-Hauz (17c),</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>PM</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><strong>Lunch.</strong><br />\r\n			<strong><em>Sightseeing tour in Bukhara</em></strong>: Visit to Registan, Ark Fortress (16 c) and Bolo-Hauz complex (18 c). Ulug Beg (15c), Abdul Aziz (17c) Madrassahs; Chor-Minor Mausoleums. Ismael Samani mausoleum (9-10c)-vault of Bukhara rulers dynasty, Chashma-Ayub Mausoleums (14 c)<br />\r\n			<strong>Dinner. </strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td rowspan=\"2\">DAY 6</td>\r\n			<td rowspan=\"2\">Bukhara – Shahrisabz – Samarkand</td>\r\n			<td>AM</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><strong>Breakfast </strong><br />\r\n			Drive to Shahrisabz.<br />\r\n			<strong><em>Sightseeing tour of Shahrisabz:</em></strong> Ak -Sarai Palace (14-15c); Dorut Tilovat: Kok - Gumbaz Mosque (15 c);</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>PM</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><strong>Lunch.</strong><br />\r\n			<strong><em>Sightseeing tour of Shahrisabz:</em></strong> Dorus Siadat: the Jekhangir Mausoleum (14c), Tamerlane\'s vault (15c).<br />\r\n			Continue to Samarkand. Arrival and accommodation at hotel. &nbsp;<br />\r\n			<strong>Distance 360 km</strong><br />\r\n			<strong>Dinner.</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td rowspan=\"2\">DAY 7</td>\r\n			<td rowspan=\"2\">Samarkand</td>\r\n			<td>AM</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><strong>Breakfast</strong><br />\r\n			<strong><em>Sightseeing tour in Samarkand:</em></strong> Gur-Emir Mausoleum (15c), Registan Ensemble (including Ulugbek (15c), Shir Dor (17c), Tillya –Kari Madrassahs (17c), Bibi Khanum Mosque. Visit to Samarkand bazaar.</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>PM</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><strong>Lunch. </strong>&nbsp;<br />\r\n			<strong><em>Sightseeing tour in Samarkand:</em></strong> Shah-i-Zinda necropolis (14-15c), “Stars above Samarkand”: tour to Ulugbek observatory (15c), “Ruins of Afrosiab” State archaeological reserve (6 BC-13 AD)<br />\r\n			<strong>Dinner.</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td rowspan=\"2\">DAY 8</td>\r\n			<td rowspan=\"2\">Samarkand – Tashkent</td>\r\n			<td>AM</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><strong>Breakfast.</strong><br />\r\n			Drive to Samarkand. <strong>Distance 310 km.</strong> Arrival and accommodation in hotel.</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>PM</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><strong>Lunch.</strong><br />\r\n			Free at leisure time.<br />\r\n			<strong>Dinner.</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>DAY 9</td>\r\n			<td>Tashkent</td>\r\n			<td>AM</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><strong>Breakfast</strong><br />\r\n			<strong>Pass the car to Peopletravel representative. Car inspection. </strong><br />\r\n			Transfer to the airport, flight back home.</p>\r\n\r\n			<p><strong><em>&nbsp;End of our services…</em></strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n', '14', 'App\Models\Tour');
INSERT INTO translations (locale, column_name, value, translatable_id, translatable_type) VALUES ('en', 'route_lines', '                           <table class=\"table tour-table-rounded\">\r\n                                 <tr>\r\n                                     <th style=\"width:8%;\">Days</th>\r\n                                     <th style=\"width:14%;\">Waypoint</th>\r\n                                     <th>Subjects of itinerary</th>\r\n                                 </tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>DAY 1</td>\r\n<td>\r\n<h3>Tashkent - Bukhara - Samarkand</h3>\r\n</td>\r\n<td>\r\n<p>Transfer to domestic airport. Flight to Bukhara at 08.50 arrival at 10.30, you’ll be met by our guide. <br /> <strong><em>Sightseeing tour in Bukhara</em></strong> Visit to Registan square, <a class=\"in_text\" title=\"Ark Fortress\" href=\"[[~767]]\">Ark Fortress</a> (16 c) and <a class=\"in_text\" title=\"Bolo-Hauz complex\" href=\"[[~692]]\">Bolo-Hauz complex</a> (18 c). <a class=\"in_text\" title=\"Ulugbeg\" href=\"[[~822]]\">Ulugbeg</a> (15c), <a class=\"in_text\" title=\"Abdul Aziz\" href=\"[[~801]]\">Abdul Aziz</a> (17c) Madrassahs; <a class=\"in_text\" title=\"Chor-Minor Mausoleums\" href=\"[[~770]]\">Chor-Minor Mausoleums</a>.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Lunch</strong><br /> <a class=\"in_text\" title=\"Ismael Samani mausoleum\" href=\"[[~786]]\">Ismael Samani mausoleum</a> (9-10c)-vault of Bukhara rulers dynasty, <a class=\"in_text\" title=\"Chashma-Ayub Mausoleums\" href=\"[[~804]]\">Chashma-Ayub Mausoleums</a> (14 c) and local Bazaar.</p>\r\n<p>After sightseeing transfer to Samarkand by vehicle, arrival to Samarkand and accommodation in hotel. <br /> <strong>Dinner. </strong></p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>DAY 2</td>\r\n<td>\r\n<h3>Samarkand - Tashkent</h3>\r\n</td>\r\n<td>\r\n<p><strong>Breakfast</strong><br /> <strong><em>Sightseeing tour in Samarkand:</em></strong> <a class=\"in_text\" title=\"Gur-Emir Mausoleum\" href=\"[[~776]]\">Gur-Emir Mausoleum</a> (15c), <a class=\"in_text\" title=\"Registan Ensemble\" href=\"[[~697]]\">Registan Ensemble</a> (including Ulugbek (15c), <a class=\"in_text\" title=\"Shir Dor\" href=\"[[~765]]\">Shir Dor</a> (17c), <a class=\"in_text\" title=\"Tillya –Kari Madrassahs\" href=\"[[~768]]\">Tillya –Kari Madrassahs</a> (17c), <a class=\"in_text\" title=\"Bibi Khanum Mosque\" href=\"[[~775]]\">Bibi Khanum Mosque</a>. Visit to Samarkand bazaar.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Lunch.</strong><br /> <strong><em>Sightseeing tour in Samarqand:</em></strong> Mausoleum of Imam Al-Bukhoriy, <a class=\"in_text\" title=\"Shah-i-Zinda necropolis\" href=\"[[~764]]\">Shah-i-Zinda necropolis</a> (14-15c), \"Stars above Samarqand\": tour to <a class=\"in_text\" title=\"Ulugbek observatory\" href=\"[[~754]]\">Ulugbek observatory</a> (15c), <br /> Transfer to Samarkand Train Station, train \"Registan\" to Tashkent at 17.00 arrival at 20.30.</p>\r\n<p><strong><em>End of our service…</em></strong></p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</table>', '15', 'App\Models\Tour');
INSERT INTO translations (locale, column_name, value, translatable_id, translatable_type) VALUES ('de', 'route_lines', '<table class=\"table tour-table-rounded\">\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th style=\"width:10%;\">TAGE</td>\r\n			<th style=\"width:14%;\">REISEROUTE</td>\r\n			<th style=\"width:8%;\">ZEIT</td>\r\n			<th>THEMEN DER REISEROUTE</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td rowspan=\"2\">1. TAG</td>\r\n			<td rowspan=\"2\">\r\n			<h3>Taschkent - Buchara - Samarkand</h3>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>Morgens</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>Umsteigen zum inländischen Flughafen. Abflug nach Buchara um 08.50, Ankunft um 10.30. Sie werden von unserem Reiseführer abgeholt.<br />\r\n			<strong><em>Stadtrundfahrt in Buchara</em></strong> Besuch in Registan, der Arche Festung (16 Jh.) und des Bolo-Hauz Komplex (18 Jh), Ulug Beg (15Jh), Abdul Aziz (17Jh) Madrassahs und das Tschor-Minor Mausoleum.<br />\r\n			<strong>Mittagessen</strong><br />\r\n			Ismael Samani Mausoleum (9-10Jh) – Die Gruft der Buchara Herrscher-Dynastie, Chashma-Ayub Mausoleums (14 Jh) und lokaler Basar.</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>NachmitTAG</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>Nach der Stadtrundfahrt. Abfahrt nach Samarkand mit dem Fahrzueg, Ankunft in Samarkand und check in im Hotel.<br />\r\n			<strong>Abendessen.</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td rowspan=\"2\">2. TAG</td>\r\n			<td rowspan=\"2\">\r\n			<h3>Samarkand - Taschkent</h3>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>Morgens</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><strong><em>Frühstück</em></strong><br />\r\n			<strong><em>Stadtrundfahrt in Samarkand:</em></strong> Gur-Emir Mausoleum (15Jh), Registan Ensemble (einschlieβlich Ulugbek (15Jh), Shir Dor (17Jh), Tillya –Kari Medressen (17Jh), Bibi Khanum Moschee. Besuch zum Basar in Samarkand.</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>NachmitTAG</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><strong>Mittagessen </strong><br />\r\n			<strong><em>Stadtrundfahrt in Samarkand:</em></strong> Mausoleum des Imam Al-Bukhoriy, Schah-i-Zinda Friedhof (14-15Jh), \"Sterne über Samarkand\": Tour zur Ulugbek Sternwarte (15Jh),<br />\r\n			Zugfahrt nach Taschkent mit dem \"Registan\" Zug um 17.00, Ankunft in Taschkent um 20.30.<br />\r\n			<br />\r\n			<strong><em>Ende unserer Leistung …</em></strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n</table>', '15', 'App\Models\Tour');
INSERT INTO translations (locale, column_name, value, translatable_id, translatable_type) VALUES ('es', 'route_lines', '<table class=\"table tour-table-rounded\">\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th style=\"width:10%;\">DÍAS</td>\r\n			<th style=\"width:14%;\">TRAYECTO</td>\r\n			<th>ITINERARIO</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td rowspan=\"3\">DÍA 1</td>\r\n			<td rowspan=\"3\">\r\n			<h3>Tashkent - Bukhara - Samarkanda</h3>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>Traslado al aeropuerto local. Vuelo a Bujara a las 08.50, llegada a las 10.30, será recibida por nuestra guía.<br />\r\n			<strong><em>Visitas en Bujara: </em></strong> Mausoleo de Ismael Samani (siglos IX-X), Mausoleo Chashma-Ayub (s XVII), Mezquita Bolo-Hauz (s.XVIII), Ciudadela Ark: Residencia de los Emires de Bukhara; Minarete Kalyan (siglo XII), Mezquita Poi-Kalyan (siglo XV), Madrassah Miri-Arab (s.XVI) en función, Emir Alim-Khan Madrassah (XX), Madrazas Ulug Beg (XV), Abdulazizxon (XVII)</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><strong>Comida</strong><br />\r\n			Mercados medievales; Toqi Zargaron, Toqi Telpakfurushon, Toqi Sarafon; Mezquita Magok-i-Attari (s.XII-XVI), Complejo Lyabi Hauz: Madraza Kukaldosh (s XVI), Khonaqo- Nadir Divanbegi (s XVII), Madraza Nadir Divanbegi (s XVII), Minarete Chor-Minor</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>Despues de las visitas traslado a Samarkanda en coche, llegada a Samarkanda y alojamiento en hotel.<br />\r\n			<strong>Cena.</strong>&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td rowspan=\"2\">DÍA 2</td>\r\n			<td rowspan=\"2\">\r\n			<h3>Samarkanda - Tashkent</h3>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><strong>Desayuno</strong><br />\r\n			<strong><em>Visitas en Samarkanda:</em></strong> Mausoleo Gur-Emir (XV), El complejo de la Plaza de Registan: Madrazas Ulugbek (XV), Sher Dor (XVII), Tillya –Kari (XVII)., Mezquita Bibi Khanum ( dedicado a la esposa de Tamerlán), Mercado Siyab</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><strong>Comida.</strong><br />\r\n			<strong><em>Visitas en Samarkanda:</em></strong>Mausoleo de Imam Al-Bukhoriy, necrópolis Shah-i-Zinda (s.XIV-XV), \"Estrellas sobre Samarqanda\": visita al observatorio de Ulugbek(s.XV).<br />\r\n			Traslado a la estación de tren de Samarkanda, tomar el tren \"Registan\" a Tashkent a las 17.00 . Llegada a las 20.30.</p>\r\n\r\n			<p><strong><em>Fin de nuestros servicios…</em></strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n</table>', '15', 'App\Models\Tour');
INSERT INTO translations (locale, column_name, value, translatable_id, translatable_type) VALUES ('fr', 'route_lines', '<table class=\"table tour-table-rounded\">\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th style=\"width:10%;\">JOURS</td>\r\n			<th style=\"width:14%;\">TRAJET</td>\r\n			<th>ITINERAIRE</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td align=\"center\" rowspan=\"3\" style=\"text-align: center;\" valign=\"top\"><strong>JOUR 1</strong></td>\r\n			<td rowspan=\"3\" valign=\"top\">\r\n			<h3 style=\"text-align: center;\">Tachkent - Boukhara - Samarcande</h3>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td valign=\"top\">\r\n			<p>Transfert à l\'aéroport domestique de Tachkent, vol pour Boukhara à 08.50. Arrivée à 10.30. Accueil et installation à l\'hôtel.<br />\r\n			<strong><em>Visite de Boukhara: </em></strong> Visite de Registan, la forteresse Ark (16 c) et complexe Bolo-Hauz (18 c). Oulougbek (15c), Abdul Aziz (17c) mausolée de Chor-Minor.</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td valign=\"top\">\r\n			<p><strong>Déjeuner</strong><br />\r\n			<strong><em>Poursuite de la visite de Boukhara:</em></strong>&nbsp;mausolée d\'Ismael Samani&nbsp; (9-10c) - caveau de la dynastie dirigeantes de Boukhara, Chashma-Ayub Mausolées (14 c)</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td valign=\"top\">\r\n			<p>Après la visite transfert à Samarcande en véhicule climatisé. Arrivée vers le soir et installation à l’hôtel.<br />\r\n			<strong>Dîner</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td align=\"center\" rowspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align: center;\" valign=\"top\"><strong>JOUR 2</strong></td>\r\n			<td rowspan=\"2\" valign=\"top\">\r\n			<h3 style=\"text-align: center;\">Samarcande - Tachkent</h3>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td valign=\"top\">\r\n			<p><strong>Petit déjeuner</strong><br />\r\n			<strong><em>Visite de Samarcande:</em></strong> mausolée Gour-Emir (15C), Registan Ensemble (y compris Oulougbek (15C), Shir Dor (de 17c), Tillia -Kari medersas (17c), la mosquée Bibi Khanoum, visite de bazar orientale ‘‘Siab’’.</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td valign=\"top\">\r\n			<p><strong>Déjeuner</strong><br />\r\n			<strong><em>Poursuite de la visite de Samarcande: </em></strong>mausolée d’Imam Al Boukhorii, nécropole Shah-i-Zinda (14-15c), \"Etoiles au-dessus Samarcande\" visite de l\'observatoire d’Oulougbek (15c), «Ruines d\'Afrasyab\" réserve archéologique d’état (6 BC-13 AD)</p>\r\n\r\n			<p>Transfert à la gare et départ pour Tachkent à 17.00. Arrivée à 19.10</p>\r\n\r\n			<p><strong><em>Fin de nos services…</em></strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n</table>\r\n\r\n\r\n', '15', 'App\Models\Tour');
INSERT INTO translations (locale, column_name, value, translatable_id, translatable_type) VALUES ('it', 'route_lines', ' <table class=\"table tour-table-rounded\">\r\n   <tbody>\r\n      <tr>\r\n         <th style=\"width:8%;\">Giorni</th>\r\n         <th style=\"width:14%;\">Tappe</th>\r\n         <th>Soggetti dell’itinerario</th>\r\n      </tr>\r\n      <tr>\r\n         <td>GIORNO 1</td>\r\n         <td>\r\n         <h3>Tashkent - Bukhara - Samarcanda</h3>\r\n         </td>\r\n         <td>\r\n         <p>Trasferimento all\'aeroporto nazionale. Volo per Bukhara alle 08:50 arrivo alle 10:30, incontro con la nostra guida.<br />\r\n         <strong><em>Giro turistico a Bukhara</em></strong> Visita alla piazza Registan, alla Fortezza dell\'Arca (16 sec) e al complesso Bolo-Hauz (18 sec). Ulugbeg (15c), Abdul Aziz (17c) Madrasse; Chor-Mausolei Minori.</p>\r\n\r\n         <p><strong>Pranzo</strong><br />\r\n         Mausoleo di Ismael Samani (9-10c)-volta della dinastia dei sovrani di Bukhara, mausolei di Chashma-Ayub (14c) e bazar locale.</p>\r\n\r\n         <p>Dopo il giro turistico trasferimento in auto a Samarcanda, arrivo a Samarcanda e sistemazione in hotel.<br />\r\n         <strong>Cena.</strong></p>\r\n         </td>\r\n      </tr>\r\n      <tr>\r\n         <td>GIORNO 2</td>\r\n         <td>\r\n         <h3>Samarcanda - Tashkent</h3>\r\n         </td>\r\n         <td>\r\n         <p><strong>Colazione</strong><br />\r\n         <strong><em>Giro turistico a Samarcanda:</em></strong> Mausoleo Gur-Emir (15c), Registan Ensemble (incluso Ulugbek (15c), Shir Dor (17c), Tillya –Kari Madrassah (17c), Moschea Bibi Khanum Visita al bazar di Samarcanda.</p>\r\n\r\n         <p><strong>Pranzo.</strong><br />\r\n         <strong><em>Giro turistico a Samarcanda:</em></strong> Mausoleo dell\'Imam Al-Bukhoriy, necropoli di Shah-i-Zinda (14-15c), \"Stelle sopra Samarcanda\": visita all\'osservatorio di Ulugbek (15c),<br />\r\n         Trasferimento alla stazione ferroviaria di Samarcanda, treno \"Registan\" per Tashkent alle 17.00 arrivo alle 20.30.</p>\r\n\r\n         <p><strong><em>Fine dei nostri servizi…</em></strong></p>\r\n         </td>\r\n      </tr>\r\n   </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n', '15', 'App\Models\Tour');
INSERT INTO translations (locale, column_name, value, translatable_id, translatable_type) VALUES ('en', 'route_lines', '                           <table class=\"table tour-table-rounded\">\r\n                                 <tr>\r\n                                     <th style=\"width:8%;\">Days</th>\r\n                                     <th style=\"width:14%;\">Waypoint</th>\r\n                                     <th>Subjects of itinerary</th>\r\n                                 </tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>DAY 1</td>\r\n<td>\r\n<h3>Tashkent - Chimgan/Charvak</h3>\r\n</td>\r\n<td>\r\n<p>Depart Tashkent to <a class=\"in_text\" title=\"Chimgan Mountains\" href=\"[[~2151]]\">Chimgan Mountains</a>, arrival and free at leisure time.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Lunch </strong></p>\r\n<p>Free at leisure time. Also possible: take a cable route, horseback riding, hiking.<br /> Transfer to Charvak, arrival and accommodation. <br /> <strong>Dinner. </strong></p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>DAY 2</td>\r\n<td>\r\n<h3>Chimgan/Charvak - Tashkent</h3>\r\n</td>\r\n<td>\r\n<p><strong>Breakfast </strong><br /> Free at leisure time, swimming</p>\r\n<p><strong>Lunch </strong><br /> Transfer back to Tashkent. <br /> <strong>Dinner </strong></p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</table>', '16', 'App\Models\Tour');
